mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"b60d65fd5f27352fba8f6b3dea9b885d18c86234","tid":2238152,"uid":102453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"黎緊HA cut budget, 呢科前景暗淡"},{"pid":"b7a84c999f3c873d46d9e1642dd7b736d614d2c5","tid":2238152,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"在醫療市場來說OT demand真的很低，因為治療的本質的病人需要性不大，即使人口有老化短期內又看不到demand會明顯提升，還要大量訓練人入行，真是很危險。<br />\n<br />\n果d吹奏既咪又係覺得呢行唔係點辛苦人工又高，呢d心態真係好差"},{"pid":"ce2b55220e51cf1adef553d5f12393b3a680f425","tid":2238152,"uid":377280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f85271582474b3a72f6992f944db1b7d25c39a8e","tid":2238152,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"dental 本來就私人市場為主<br />\nchiro 中醫 政府醫院冇相關職位<br />\n其他allied health/nursing 點解出private就因為外面人工高好多 工作又相對輕鬆d<br />\n<br />\nOT 響HA入面本來就係好輕鬆嘅職業 (vs Physio) 外面人工又唔係話高好多 吸引唔到人出去做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53fe9f8ee49d7687bc10b1be1dd0913c0a8bcb4","tid":2238152,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce2b55220e51cf1adef553d5f12393b3a680f425","tid":2238152,"uid":377280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f85271582474b3a72f6992f944db1b7d25c39a8e","tid":2238152,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"dental 本來就私人市場為主<br />\nchiro 中醫 政府醫院冇相關職位<br />\n其他allied health/nursing 點解出private就因為外面人工高好多 工作又相對輕鬆d<br />\n<br />\nOT 響HA入面本來就係好輕鬆嘅職業 (vs Physio) 外面人工又唔係話高好多 吸引唔到人出去做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T03:16:40.000Z","msg":"NGO幾時變成公營<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />非政府組織喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近年畢業生基本上都係衝入HA 好少人去ngo做<br />\n唔加budget 又點 而家都係全部人入到行 <br />\n加多10個畢業生 都未至於飽和啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更何況而家移民潮 個個都想走<br />\n外國讀OT 應該越來越多會選擇直接移民<br />\n香港做緊HA個班又plan緊移民<br />\n真係驚咪讀RT optometry 少人競爭<br />\n<br />\n開唔開到clinic都是但啦<br />\n醫院返工人工都已經幾好<br />\n30-80k人工 work-life balance<br />\n<br />\n開clinic 其實好麻煩<br />\n又要客源 又要有一定功力<br />\n道理就好似創業 唔係個個做到發達"},{"pid":"4b024aaec7671af9748763343e33d933cfb7f904","tid":2238152,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:09:14.000Z","msg":"D ngo請d pt ot係做part time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每日做幾個鐘"}]}